query:
SELECT g.id as gestorId, u.name as gestorNome, gl.lojaId, l.nome as lojaNome
FROM gestores g
INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
LEFT JOIN gestor_lojas gl ON g.id = gl.gestorId
LEFT JOIN lojas l ON gl.lojaId = l.id
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Fábio%' OR u.name LIKE '%Fabio%';
